  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, our approach minimizes resource consumption and operational downtime, which are significant challenges associated with comprehensive model retraining.",
    "This comparison underscores the efficiency and effectiveness of our methodology, highlighting its potential to serve as a benchmark for future endeavors in model updating.",
    "Challenges EncounteredThroughout the implementation and evaluation of the incremental knowledge enrichment process, several challenges were encountered.",
    "The scalability of the dynamic linking mechanism and the maintenance of model performance amidst the continuous influx of new information were particularly significant.",
    "Addressing these challenges required innovative architectural adjustments and the development of an adaptive learning rate mechanism."
